'''Ajdir''' (s [[Tasrɣint|Taserɣint]]: مدينة أجدير) tgat yan [[iɣrm]] illan g [[Agafay|ugafay]] n [[Lmɣrib]], g [[Tamnaḍt|tmnaḍt]] n [[Rrif|Arrif]]. ittwassn iɣrm n Ajdir mas iga [[tamazirt]] n [[Muḥmmad n Ɛbdlkrim Axṭṭab|Mulay Muḥand]], ig ula adɣar sg-d ifka [[Agllid|ugllid]] [[Muḥmmad VI|Muḥmmad wis 6]] taguri n usuded n [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|Tmaziɣt]] g Tmazirt n Lmɣrib

==Amawal : ==
